OOC: Talon, Ravenchief and Lord Perseus were supposed to be outside the
power room where radio doesn&#39;t reach.  But I guess a radio booster could be
active.

BIC:

The problem was simple.  The reactor had simply been shut down.

&quot;The Maximals must have been totally unprepared for Jhaxius&#39; attack.  They
shut down the power and closed the blast doors as a last ditch effort to
prevent the enemy from using the base,&quot; said Perseus.  &quot;What they failed to
realize is that he didn&#39;t want this base, he wanted to kill the maximals
inside.&quot;

Ravenchief opened the glass cover and pressed the giant red button on the
reactor controls, but nothing happened.

&quot;That&#39;s the emergency shut off,  pull up on the switch.&quot;

Ravenchief pulled and there was a sudden wirring sound as lights and
equipement turned on all over the base.  They were suddenly startled by a
loud voice:

&quot;SENTINEL ONLINE: EXTERIOR WEAPONS SYSTEM AND SHIELDS, ENTRY DOORS, INTERNAL
CANNONS, NON-OPERATIONAL.  ENEMY SIGNATURES DETECTED.&quot;

Meanwhile...

Salveo keyed the radio in the shuttle.

&quot;Legacy, this is Pacificus Maximal Leutienant Salveo.  We have encountered
minion activity within this base, perhaps a trap set for our eventual
return.&quot;

He suddenly noticed the scanners picking up power activity within the base.

&quot;Lord Perseus, is the base secure?&quot;

&quot;We have not encountered any resistence in the lower base.  Start
offloading, our gear into the large room by the command center, all personel
to the entrance area.&quot;

On Feb 13, 2010 1:26 PM, &quot;Super Cyclonus&quot; &lt;supercyclonus@...&gt; wrote:

&gt;Talon:
&gt;
&gt;&quot;Report at my location and we can start to secire the
&gt;area&quot; said talon

&quot;Understood.&quot; Legacy intoned from his aerial position, his voice cold and
unfeeling over the transmission lines.

Above the old Maximal base the military satellite that was Legacy shifted
and contorted as it changed forms, the sound of gears moving together could
be heard as it quickly assumed its armored robotic mode. Boosters flare for
a moment allowing Legacy to touch down and look around, his single optic
shifted colors then resuming its typical crimson glow.

Turning his rather bulky form Legacy quickly made his way to Talon&#39;s
position, &quot;I see no evidence of an attack in progress, although there are
residual energy patterns here.&quot; Legacy turned his cold gaze on talon, &quot;Where
are the minions?&quot;

(OOC: I am not sure where the other Maximals are, or where Talon is in
relation to all of this, so I was somewhat vague. This should open to anyone
that is in the area I would guess??)

Preston
(Legacy)





